    <briefdescription>
<para>This is the primary header file that users should include to access the hipDNN frontend API. It provides a high-level C++ interface for building and executing deep learning computational graphs on AMD GPUs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The hipDNN Frontend provides a graph-based API for constructing deep learning operations including:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Convolution operations (forward, data gradient, weight gradient)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Batch normalization (forward, backward, inference)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Pointwise/element-wise operations</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Matrix multiplication</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<sect1 id="hipdnn__frontend_8hpp_1usage">
<title>Basic usage</title>
